\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs26\b0\i0 Before the poker game commences, bursting with enthusiasm and excitement, Evan shares what he sees as an innovative relationship strategy. One that eliminates the negative aspects of the traditional dating process and also mitigates, what he sees as the inevitable deterioration of a positive relationship. He's determined that true love only comes once in a lifetime, and he had his one-shot at true love that ended in divorce. So instead of looking for unattainable true love and avoiding endless dating, he's come up with a plan to have a great relationship for one year and then terminating it before the relationship begins to deteriorate.}
