\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {Horrified by Evan's relationship plan, but wanting to support and protect her brother, who is clearly going to follow through with his plan, A reluctant Liz insisted that some rules and guidelines be established. Liz says these rules and guidelines are meant not only to protect Evan, but any woman who gets reeled into his crazy plan.  She enlists the help of the poker party guests, assigning each member of the poker party was assigned the task of coming up with at least one rule.}}